{"word":"Asher","slug":"asher","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Asher</b> <a href=\"#/H836\">H836</a> <br/> 1. Son of Jacob, by Zilpah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=13'>Gen 30:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=26'>Gen 35:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=20'>Gen 49:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=1&verse=4'>Exo 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=2'>1Ch 2:2</a><br/> 2. Descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=46&verse=17'>Gen 46:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=47'>Num 26:47</a><br/> 3. Tribe of:<br/> - Census of, by families<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=41'>Num 1:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=47'>Num 26:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=7&verse=40'>1Ch 7:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=36'>1Ch 12:36</a> <br/> - Station of, in camp<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=25'>Num 2:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=27'>Num 2:27</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning, by Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=25'>Deu 33:25</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning, by John<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=7&verse=6'>Rev 7:6</a> <br/> - Allotment to, of land in Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=31'>Jos 19:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=48&verse=2'>Eze 48:2</a> <br/> - Upbraided by Deborah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=5&verse=17'>Jdg 5:17</a> <br/> - Summoned by Gideon<br/> <a href='http